Post GoD SK AAs<br />
AA Skill - #Levels - (Cost progression for Level(s))<br />
<br />
-Swift Journey - 2 - (5/10)<br />
Description: This ability will slightly modify your base run speed. This modification does NOT stack with movement rate spell effects<br />
Requirement: Run 3<br />
Effect: 10% per level. Max: 50% along with run 3.<br />
<br />
-Convalescence - 2 - (3/6?)<br />
Description:This ability raises your regeneration ability by 1 point per ability level.<br />
Effect: +1 innate hp regeneration per level. Max: +2 innate hp regeneration.<br />
<br />
-Lasting Breath - 2 - (2/4?)<br />
Description: This ability increases the amount of air you can hold in your lungs.<br />
Effect: ?<br />
<br />
-PackRat - 5 - (3/6?/9?/12?/15?)<br />
Description: Each rank in this ability improves the efficiency with which you store your gear, effectively reducing your overall weight. <br />
Effect: ?<br />
<br />
-Weapon Affinty - 5 - (2/4/6/8/10)<br />
Description: Through years of practice, you develop a close bond with your weapons. This affinity allows you to gain enhanced performance from your weapons in the form of an increased rate at which it triggers effects.<br />
Effect: Estimated +10% to proc per level, initial tests show that it will not effect procs added to weapons by spells. Max: 50%?<br />
<br />
-Persistant Casting - 3 - (3/6/9)<br />
Description: Your highly developed concentration creates the possibility of continuing to cast spells while stunned. Increased ranks in this ability increase the chance that your spells will not be interrupted by stuns. <br />
Effect: Level 3 = 15% chance? If so, maybe 5% per level?<br />
<br />
-Pet Affinity - 1 - (20)<br />
Description: This ability makes your summoned pets a valid target for beneficial group spells.<br />
Effect: Same as description.<br />
<br />
-Critical Affliction - 3 - (5/10/15)<br />
Description: This ability grants damage-over-time spells the chance to have a critical effect for each tick they are active.Effect: Level 3: 9-10% chance (from necro thread) for 2x dmg? Initial test shows that there is no crit message.. Just 2x damage.<br />
<br />
-Death's Fury - 5 - (3/3/3/3/3)<br />
Description: Grants our pet melee crit ability and increase the chance to crit.<br />
Effect: ?<br />
<br />
-Immobilizing Bash - 3 - (3/6/9)<br />
Description: Increase the chance to stun an npc on successful bash. <br />
Effect: ?<br />
<br />
-Vicious Smash - 5 - (3/6/9/12/15)<br />
Description: Adds a damage bonus to ANY bash.<br />
Effect: +5 DB(Damage Bonus) per level. Max: 25 DB. Same strength toward 2h bash and shield bash.<br />
<br />
-Improved Con. of the Soul - 2 - (6/12?)<br />
Description: Add more hp to your lifetap HT.<br />
Effect: +200 hp per level. Max: +400 hp.<br />
<br />
-Intense Hatred - 5 - (3/6/9/12/15)<br />
Description: Add innate damage shield (DS).<br />
Requirement: DS buff on<br />
Effect: 3 ds per level. Max: 15 ds. Activate only if your DS buff is on.<br />
